  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    A new approach to information warfare: @HutEighteen
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">An information warfare network, known as @HutEighteen, was launched in partnership with the Defence Academy of the United Kingdom. </p>

  </div>
</div>

